# Docs

- Use bullet points and tables; avoid long prose walls
- DESIGN.md: specific failure-mode answers (not generic "we use locking")
- AI_USAGE.md: honest tools (Claude web = planning, Cursor = code); three real decisions
- No TBD except README Demo Video link before submission
- Keep API.md in sync with actual routes and status codes
